me.timothy.tests.database

Class FullnameMappingTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.timothy.tests.database.FullnameMappingTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MysqlFullnameMappingTest

    public class FullnameMappingTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes tests focused on the FullnameMapping in a mapping database. The database must be completely empty after setup every time. The database will be modified - it should point at a test database.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Concrete Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void testContains()
      Tests that contains will return true for Strings that are equal, and false for fullnames that are not in the database, regardless of if they are alike in the MySQL sense.
      void testSave()
      Tests that saving fullnames will set their id to a strictly positive number, and that the fullname can be fetched again with fetchAll()
      void testTest()
      Verifies the test is setup correctly by ensuring the database is not null
